            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0386-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-3a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">This is not something a common person can understand;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-3a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">how could someone of shallow understanding be able to investigate it thoroughly?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">When we speak of "Zi" (子, Master),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">it is an excellent honorific for someone of virtue.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">In ancient times, people called teachers "Zi."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">It also means that "Zi" is the title of a book,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">not just the collective name for three sections,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">but also a common title for the hundred schools of thought.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">As for what is meant by "Inner Chapters,"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">"Inner" is named in relation to "Outer," to establish a distinction.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">"Chapter" (篇) means a collection of bamboo slips arranged together.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">In ancient times, they scraped bamboo to make slips,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">and used leather to bind them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">Arranging the slips creates a chapter,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">just as connecting sheets of paper today creates a scroll.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">Therefore, Yuan Kai said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">"Important matters are recorded on bamboo tablets,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">while minor matters are recorded on simple slips."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">"Inner" discusses fundamental principles,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">while "Outer" speaks of events and traces.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">Though events are clearly visible,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">they cannot be understood without principle;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">though principles are profound and subtle,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">they cannot be revealed without events.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">Wanting to first clarify the subtle principles,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">therefore, we first present the Inner Chapters.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">The Inner Chapters contain profound principles,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">therefore, we separately establish the titles of each chapter outside the main text.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">Guo Xiang annotates them immediately below the title,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">such as "Carefree Wandering" and "On Leveling All Things."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">From the Outer Chapters onward,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">we take the first two characters of the chapter to be its title,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-4a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">such as "Webbed Toes" and "Horses' Hooves."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_002-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:27:44.128+09:00">As for what is meant by "Carefree Wandering" (逍遙遊),</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
